narration_text: #C C picks up a bottle and a soap
#C C washes the bowl with a soap and a piece of cloth
#C C wipes the hand with a napkin
#C C drops the napkin on top of a bowl
#C C picks the napkin and bowl
#C C dries the bowl with a napkin
#C C moves the napkin to another hand
#C C paces the napkin on the handle of the gas cooker
#C C places a bowl inside a cupboard
#C C picks the plate inside the cupboard
#C C dries the knife with a napkin
#C C picks a bottle from the fridge
#C C places the bottle on a sink
#C C picks up a bag on the chair
#c c picks tongs on the kitchen counter top
#c c puts the serving spoon down
